LIMB - Lithesome Interactive Media Builder -  $Id: INSTALL 257 2004-05-17 09:30:34Z server $
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

http://limb-project.com

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OS : OS independent

Web Server: Apache  1.3+ (configured  with  AllowOverride  All for directory where
you plan to place your project) with PHP installed as a module(you can use PHP
installed as CGI also using mod_rewrite quirks, however this feature is not documented,
use it at your own risk!)

Development Environment: PHP 4.2+

Database: MySQL 3.23+ (4.0+ more preferred)
(LIMB should work on 3.23+ with InnoDB support. LIMB also uses full text search
capabilities of 3.23+ version)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 WHAT'S NEXT???
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please refer to the further install instructions available in your LIMB based
project.